---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="离线模式 - Kailash 2026" description="您处于离线状态，但仍可查看已缓存的基本朝圣信息。">
  <section class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center bg-kailash-light px-4">
    <div class="text-center max-w-lg mx-auto py-20">
      <div class="text-6xl mb-6">🏔️</div>
      <h1 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-4">当前离线</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-2">您没有网络连接</p>
      <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">但不用担心——核心朝圣指南和路线信息仍可查看</p>

      <div class="grid gap-4">
        <a href="/" class="block bg-kailash-dark text-white px-6 py-4 rounded-xl font-medium hover:bg-kailash-stone transition">
          返回首页
        </a>
        <a href="/guide" class="block bg-white text-kailash-dark px-6 py-4 rounded-xl font-medium border border-gray-200 hover:border-kailash-gold transition">
          朝圣攻略（已缓存）
        </a>
        <a href="/routes" class="block bg-white text-kailash-dark px-6 py-4 rounded-xl font-medium border border-gray-200 hover:border-kailash-gold transition">
          转山路线（已缓存）
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-8">
        重新联网后将自动更新内容。冈仁波齐永远在这里等您。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
